Title: Incense Gratification
Description:
That's some real potent incense you made! Usually it takes time to get this good!

Now, I've got some of my own brewing to do, so you're gonna have to go out and set those up by yourself.

Once you're finished I'm sure Honeypelt will be mighty keen on hearing about it! Best follow up with her when you're done.
ObjectivesText: Place 9 Missing Incense in Zaralek Cavern.
